<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3942905>
    dc:description "Figure 8.1. (Left) Tyrannosaurus \"x\" (AMNH 5027). (Right) Tyrannosaurus rex (BHI3033)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3942905/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3942907>
    dc:description "Figure 8.2. Medial view of right dentary of the type Tyrannosaurus rex CM 9380. Note the incisiform first dentary tooth." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3942907/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3942909>
    dc:description "Figure 8.3. Left and right first dentary teeth of Tyrannosaurus rex BHI 3033. (A) Lateral view. (B) Posterior view. Note that both serrations are exposed in the posterior view, creating the typical tyrannosaurid D-shaped cross section. " ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3942909/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3942911>
    dc:description "Figure 8.4. Dorsal view of the anterior portion of the left dentary of Tyrannosaurus rex CM 9380 preserving small first dentary tooth DT1 and large second dentary tooth DT2." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3942911/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3942913>
    dc:description "Figure 8.5. Dorsal view of the anterior portion of the left dentary of Tyrannosaurus \"x\" (Samson) preserving small alveoli for DT1 and DT2 and a large alveolus for the third dentary tooth DT3" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3942913/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3942915>
    dc:description "Figure 8.6. Lateral view of the left lachrymals of (A) Tyrannosaurus \"x\" AMNH 5027 and (B) Tyrannosaurus rex BHI 3033. Note the larger lateral pneumatic foramen on T. rex." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3942915/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3942917>
    dc:description "Figure 8.7. Lachrymal length vs. lachrymal foramina length." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3942917/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3942919>
    dc:description "Figure 8.8. Type specimen of Nanotyrannus lancensis CMNH 7541." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3942919/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3942921>
    dc:description "Figure 8.9. Examples of measurement techniques used in this study." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3942921/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3942923>
    dc:description "Figure 8.10. Anterior view of right metatarsal II of (A) gracile (BHI 3033) and (B) robust (TCM 2001.90.1) morphotypes" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3942923/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3942925>
    dc:description "Figure 8.11. Metatarsal II length vs. circumference." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3942925/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3942927>
    dc:description "Figure 8.12. Ilium length vs. height." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3942927/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3942929>
    dc:description "Figure 8.13. Anterior view of (A) left humerus of gracile (BHI 6230) and (B) right humerus of robust (FMNH PR2081) morphotypes" ;
